{"type":"message","id":"7a685fba","parentId":"9d979ed9","timestamp":"2026-03-09T10:43:50.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文件不存在，可能是之前的代码执行没有真正保存文件，或者文件被清理了。让我重新下载一张蔡文姬的图片。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_41e9d138f0fb45f3bed5c8d0","name":"aliyun_code_interpreter","arguments":{"arguments":{"code":"import requests\nimport os\n\n# 蔡文姬图片 URL（使用稳定的图床链接）\nimg_urls = [\n    \"https://game.gtimg.cn/images/yxzj/img201606/skin/hero-info/113/113-bigskin-1.jpg\",\n    \"https://game.gtimg.cn/images/yxzj/img201606/hero/img/113.png\"\n]\n\nimg_dir = '/root/.openclaw/workspace/images'\nos.makedirs(img_dir, exist_ok=True)\n\nheaders = {\n    'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n    'Referer': 'https://pvp.qq.com/'\n}\n\nfor i, url in enumerate(img_urls):\n    try:\n        response = requests.get(url, headers=headers, timeout=15)\n        if response.status_code == 200 and len(response.content) > 1000:\n            img_path = f\"{img_dir}/caiwenji_{i}.jpg\"\n            with open(img_path, 'wb') as f:\n                f.write(response.content)\n            print(f\"成功下载：{img_path}\")\n            print(f\"文件大小：{len(response.content)} bytes\")\n            break\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"下载失败 {url}: {e}\")\nelse:\n    print(\"所有链接都下载失败\")"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773053021916}}
